videos.description: Andrew Jones makes a nice pass to Kai Jones, who throws down a loud dunk in transition.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Jones makes noise with powerful slam) 2020/03/07

videos.headline: Jones makes noise with powerful slam

videos.description: Lindy Waters III finds Kalib Boone on his way to the basket, and Boone elevates for the wide-open dunk.
